---
import { Image } from "astro:assets";
import musculacionBg from "../../assets/class-musculacion.jpg";
import funcionalBg from "../../assets/class-funcional.jpg";
import spinningBg from "../../assets/class-spinning.jpg";
import personalBg from "../../assets/class-personal.jpg";
import zumbaBg from "../../assets/class-zumba.jpg";
---

<section class="classes" id="clases" data-animate>
  <div class="classes__bg-text" aria-hidden="true">ENTRENÁ</div>

  <div class="classes__container">
    <header class="classes__header">
      <p class="classes__tag" data-animate>// CLASES</p>
      <h2 class="classes__title" data-animate>
        <span class="classes__title-line">ELEGÍ TU </span>
        <span class="classes__title-line classes__title-line--accent">CAMINO</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="classes__desc" data-animate>
        Desde musculación hasta zumba, tenemos lo que necesitás para moverte. Clases en grupo o entrenamiento solo, siempre con un profe al lado.
      </p>
    </header>

    <div class="classes__grid">
      <article class="classes__item" data-animate>
        <Image src={musculacionBg} alt="Persona levantando pesas en la sala de musculación" class="classes__item-bg" width={800} height={600} />
        <span class="classes__item-overlay" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        <span class="classes__item-num" aria-hidden="true">01</span>
        <div class="classes__item-body">
          <h3 class="classes__item-title">MUSCULACIÓN</h3>
          <p class="classes__item-desc">Libre y con máquinas. Todo el equipamiento para que trabajes cada grupo muscular a tu ritmo.</p>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="classes__item" data-animate>
        <Image src={funcionalBg} alt="Grupo haciendo ejercicios funcionales" class="classes__item-bg" width={800} height={600} />
        <span class="classes__item-overlay" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        <span class="classes__item-num" aria-hidden="true">02</span>
        <div class="classes__item-body">
          <h3 class="classes__item-title">FUNCIONALES GRUPALES</h3>
          <p class="classes__item-desc">Entrenamiento en grupo de alta intensidad. Quemas calorías, ganás fuerza y te llevás la energía del equipo.</p>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="classes__item" data-animate>
        <Image src={spinningBg} alt="Clase de spinning en el gimnasio" class="classes__item-bg" width={800} height={600} />
        <span class="classes__item-overlay" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        <span class="classes__item-num" aria-hidden="true">03</span>
        <div class="classes__item-body">
          <h3 class="classes__item-title">SPINNING</h3>
          <p class="classes__item-desc">Subite a la bici y pedaléa al ritmo de la música. Clases guiadas que te llevan al límite.</p>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="classes__item" data-animate>
        <Image src={personalBg} alt="Entrenador personal trabajando uno a uno con un alumno" class="classes__item-bg" width={800} height={600} />
        <span class="classes__item-overlay" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        <span class="classes__item-num" aria-hidden="true">04</span>
        <div class="classes__item-body">
          <h3 class="classes__item-title">PERSONAL TRAINER</h3>
          <p class="classes__item-desc">Uno a uno con un entrenador que arma un plan a tu medida. Resultados más rápido, con seguimiento real.</p>
        </div>
      </article>

      <article class="classes__item" data-animate>
        <Image src={zumbaBg} alt="Personas bailando zumba en una clase grupal" class="classes__item-bg" width={800} height={600} />
        <span class="classes__item-overlay" aria-hidden="true"></span>
        <span class="classes__item-num" aria-hidden="true">05</span>
        <div class="classes__item-body">
          <h3 class="classes__item-title">ZUMBA</h3>
          <p class="classes__item-desc">Baile y fitness se encuentran. La forma más divertida de moverte, sudar y soltarte.</p>
        </div>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<section class="plans" id="planes" data-animate>
  <div class="plans__bg-text" aria-hidden="true">PLANES</div>

  <div class="plans__container">
    <header class="plans__header">
      <p class="plans__tag" data-animate>// PLANES</p>
      <h2 class="plans__title" data-animate>
        <span class="plans__title-line">ELEGÍ TU</span>
        <span class="plans__title-line plans__title-line--accent">INTENSIDAD</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="plans__desc" data-animate>Sin permanencia. Sin letra chica. Elegí el plan que mejor se adapte a tu meta y empezá cuando quieras.</p>
    </header>

    <div class="plans__grid">
      <article class="plans__card" data-animate>
        <p class="plans__card-label">01 / BÁSICO</p>
        <p class="plans__card-name">ENTRENÁ LIBRE</p>
        <p class="plans__card-price"><span class="plans__card-price-num">$25.000</span> /MES</p>
        <ul class="plans__card-features">
          <li class="plans__card-feature">
            <span class="plans__card-check" aria-hidden="true">✓</span>
            Acceso a sala de musculación
          </li>
          <li class="plans__card-feature">
            <span class="plans__card-check" aria-hidden="true">✓</span>
            Horario libre
          </li>
          <li class="plans__card-feature">
            <span class="plans__card-check" aria-hidden="true">✓</span>
            Vestuarios y lockers
          </li>
        </ul>
        <a href="https://wa.me/541123456789?text=Hola%20quiero%20info%20sobre%20el%20plan%20b%C3%A1sico" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="plans__card-btn plans__card-btn--outline">ELEGIR BÁSICO</a>
      </article>

      <article class="plans__card plans__card--featured" data-animate>
        <span class="plans__card-badge">MÁS ELEGIDO</span>
        <p class="plans__card-label">02 / FULL</p>
        <p class="plans__card-name">TODO INCLUIDO</p>
        <p class="plans__card-price"><span class="plans__card-price-num">$38.000</span> /MES</p>
        <ul class="plans__card-features">
          <li class="plans__card-feature">
            <span class="plans__card-check" aria-hidden="true">✓</span>
            Musculación + todas las clases grupales
          </li>
          <li class="plans__card-feature">
            <span class="plans__card-check" aria-hidden="true">✓</span>
            Spinning, funcional y zumba
          </li>
          <li class="plans__card-feature">
            <span class="plans__card-check" aria-hidden="true">✓</span>
            Evaluación física mensual
          </li>
          <li class="plans__card-feature">
            <span class="plans__card-check" aria-hidden="true">✓</span>
            Acceso a la app de seguimiento
          </li>
        </ul>
        <a href="https://wa.me/541123456789?text=Hola%20quiero%20info%20sobre%20el%20plan%20full" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="plans__card-btn plans__card-btn--primary">ELEGIR FULL</a>
      </article>

      <article class="plans__card" data-animate>
        <p class="plans__card-label">03 / PERSONALIZADO</p>
        <p class="plans__card-name">UNO A UNO</p>
        <p class="plans__card-price"><span class="plans__card-price-num">$65.000</span> /MES</p>
        <ul class="plans__card-features">
          <li class="plans__card-feature">
            <span class="plans__card-check" aria-hidden="true">✓</span>
            Entrenador personal dedicado
          </li>
          <li class="plans__card-feature">
            <span class="plans__card-check" aria-hidden="true">✓</span>
            Plan 100% a tu medida
          </li>
          <li class="plans__card-feature">
            <span class="plans__card-check" aria-hidden="true">✓</span>
            Seguimiento semanal de resultados
          </li>
          <li class="plans__card-feature">
            <span class="plans__card-check" aria-hidden="true">✓</span>
            Acceso full a todas las clases
          </li>
        </ul>
        <a href="https://wa.me/541123456789?text=Hola%20quiero%20info%20sobre%20el%20plan%20personalizado" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="plans__card-btn plans__card-btn--outline">ELEGIR PERSONALIZADO</a>
      </article>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  /* ============ CLASSES SECTION ============ */
  .classes {
    position: relative;
    padding: var(--space-xl) var(--container-padding);
    background: var(--color-bg);
    overflow: hidden;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .classes__bg-text {
    position: absolute;
    top: 3rem;
    right: -0.1em;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(5rem, 22vw, 18rem);
    font-weight: var(--fw-extrablack);
    color: transparent;
    -webkit-text-stroke: 1px var(--color-border);
    opacity: 0.1;
    white-space: nowrap;
    pointer-events: none;
    user-select: none;
    line-height: 1;
    z-index: 0;
  }

  .classes__container {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    max-width: var(--container-max);
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .classes__tag {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    font-weight: var(--fw-semibold);
    letter-spacing: var(--tracking-widest);
    color: var(--color-accent);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .classes__title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-weight: var(--fw-extrablack);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    line-height: 0.92;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .classes__title-line {
    display: block;
    font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 8vw, 4.5rem);
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .classes__title-line--accent {
    color: var(--color-accent);
  }

  .classes__desc {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    max-width: 520px;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .classes__grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-md);
  }

  .classes__item {
    position: relative;
    min-height: 220px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-end;
    gap: var(--space-lg);
    padding: var(--space-lg);
    background-color: #111;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    overflow: hidden;
    transition: border-color var(--transition-fast), transform var(--transition-fast);
  }

  .classes__item:hover {
    border-color: var(--color-accent);
    transform: scale(1.02);
  }

  .classes__item-bg {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    width: 100%;
    height: 100%;
    display: block;
    object-fit: cover;
    z-index: 0;
  }

  .classes__item-overlay {
    position: absolute;
    inset: 0;
    background: linear-gradient(180deg, transparent 0%, rgba(0,0,0,0.45) 40%, rgba(0,0,0,0.85) 100%);
    pointer-events: none;
    z-index: 1;
  }

  .classes__item-num {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    font-weight: var(--fw-bold);
    color: var(--color-accent);
    letter-spacing: var(--tracking-wide);
    flex-shrink: 0;
    margin-bottom: 0.15rem;
  }

  .classes__item-body {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 2;
    flex: 1;
  }

  .classes__item-title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    font-weight: var(--fw-bold);
    color: var(--color-text);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: var(--tracking-wide);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xs);
  }

  .classes__item-desc {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    line-height: 1.6;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
  }

  .classes__tag {
    transition-delay: 0s;
  }

  .classes__title {
    transition-delay: 0.1s;
  }

  .classes__desc {
    transition-delay: 0.15s;
  }

  .classes__item:nth-child(1) { transition-delay: 0.2s; }
  .classes__item:nth-child(2) { transition-delay: 0.27s; }
  .classes__item:nth-child(3) { transition-delay: 0.34s; }
  .classes__item:nth-child(4) { transition-delay: 0.41s; }
  .classes__item:nth-child(5) { transition-delay: 0.48s; }

  /* ============ PLANS SECTION ============ */
  .plans {
    position: relative;
    padding: var(--space-xl) var(--container-padding);
    background: var(--color-bg);
    overflow: hidden;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .plans__bg-text {
    position: absolute;
    top: 50%;
    left: -0.1em;
    transform: translateY(-50%);
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(5rem, 22vw, 18rem);
    font-weight: var(--fw-extrablack);
    color: transparent;
    -webkit-text-stroke: 1px var(--color-border);
    opacity: 0.1;
    white-space: nowrap;
    pointer-events: none;
    user-select: none;
    line-height: 1;
    z-index: 0;
  }

  .plans__container {
    position: relative;
    z-index: 1;
    max-width: var(--container-max);
    margin: 0 auto;
  }

  .plans__tag {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    font-weight: var(--fw-semibold);
    letter-spacing: var(--tracking-widest);
    color: var(--color-accent);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .plans__title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-weight: var(--fw-extrablack);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    line-height: 0.92;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
  }

  .plans__title-line {
    display: block;
    font-size: clamp(2.2rem, 8vw, 4.5rem);
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  .plans__title-line--accent {
    color: var(--color-accent);
  }

  .plans__desc {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    line-height: 1.7;
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    max-width: 520px;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .plans__grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-md);
    align-items: start;
  }

  .plans__card {
    position: relative;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    padding: var(--space-xl) var(--space-lg);
    background: var(--color-bg-card);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    transition: border-color var(--transition-fast), transform var(--transition-fast);
  }

  .plans__card:hover {
    border-color: var(--color-text-dim);
    transform: translateY(-4px);
  }

  .plans__card--featured {
    border-color: var(--color-accent);
    background: var(--color-bg-elevated);
  }

  .plans__card--featured:hover {
    border-color: var(--color-accent-hover);
  }

  .plans__card-badge {
    position: absolute;
    top: 0;
    left: 50%;
    transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    font-weight: var(--fw-bold);
    letter-spacing: var(--tracking-wide);
    color: var(--color-text);
    background: var(--color-accent);
    padding: 0.4rem 1rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
    white-space: nowrap;
  }

  .plans__card-label {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    font-weight: var(--fw-semibold);
    letter-spacing: var(--tracking-wider);
    color: var(--color-text-dim);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .plans__card-name {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-2xl);
    font-weight: var(--fw-black);
    color: var(--color-text);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: var(--tracking-tight);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
  }

  .plans__card-price {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    font-weight: var(--fw-semibold);
    letter-spacing: var(--tracking-wider);
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-lg);
    padding-bottom: var(--space-lg);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .plans__card-price-num {
    font-size: var(--text-4xl);
    font-weight: var(--fw-extrablack);
    color: var(--color-text);
    letter-spacing: var(--tracking-tight);
  }

  .plans__card-features {
    list-style: none;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-sm);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);
    flex: 1;
  }

  .plans__card-feature {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
    display: flex;
    align-items: flex-start;
    gap: var(--space-sm);
  }

  .plans__card-check {
    color: var(--color-accent);
    font-weight: var(--fw-bold);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .plans__card-btn {
    display: block;
    width: 100%;
    text-align: center;
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    font-weight: var(--fw-bold);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: var(--tracking-wide);
    padding: 1rem 2rem;
    cursor: pointer;
    transition: all var(--transition-fast);
  }

  .plans__card-btn--outline {
    background: transparent;
    color: var(--color-text);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .plans__card-btn--outline:hover {
    border-color: var(--color-text);
    background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.05);
  }

  .plans__card-btn--primary {
    background: var(--color-accent);
    color: var(--color-text);
    border: none;
  }

  .plans__card-btn--primary:hover {
    background: var(--color-accent-hover);
  }

  .plans__tag {
    transition-delay: 0s;
  }

  .plans__title {
    transition-delay: 0.1s;
  }

  .plans__desc {
    transition-delay: 0.15s;
  }

  .plans__card:nth-child(1) { transition-delay: 0.2s; }
  .plans__card:nth-child(2) { transition-delay: 0.3s; }
  .plans__card:nth-child(3) { transition-delay: 0.4s; }

  /* ============ RESPONSIVE ============ */
  @media (min-width: 768px) {
    .classes {
      padding: var(--space-2xl) var(--container-padding);
    }

    .classes__grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
    }

    .classes__item {
      min-height: 260px;
    }

    .plans {
      padding: var(--space-2xl) var(--container-padding);
    }
  }

  @media (min-width: 1024px) {
    .classes {
      padding: var(--space-2xl) var(--container-padding);
    }

    .classes__header {
      max-width: 600px;
    }

    .plans {
      padding: var(--space-2xl) var(--container-padding);
    }

    .plans__grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr 1fr;
      gap: var(--space-lg);
    }

    .plans__card--featured {
      transform: scale(1.05);
    }

    .plans__card--featured:hover {
      transform: scale(1.05) translateY(-4px);
    }
  }
</style>
